item.description:
Apple hardware has been an unqualified success for Apple over the past decade+. The whole software stack, however, is lagging significantly behind. We are only scratching the surface of what Apple devices can deliver, especially on the AI/ML front. It will be interesting to see if there will be any significant course changes over the next few years.

